unbind r                    # This clears any existing 'r' command
bind r source-file ~/.tmux.conf  # This tells tmux: "If I hit Prefix, then r, reload"
How to know it worked:
When you hit that sequence, you should see a message at the bottom of your screen saying:

"thunder config 0.3 loaded for tmux"

This happens because of the very first line in your file: display-message "thunder config 0.3 loaded for tmux". If you don't see that message, the reload didn't trigger.

